Notes

Source: vignettes/Notes.Rmd
Notes.Rmd
library(comlandr)

For details of its use see the tech-doc

  1. Either pulls data from data tables (~15 mins) or reads in from a previous pull
  2. aggregate landings by stat area or EPU (multiple stat areas)
  3. include foreign landings as defined by NAFO
  4. disaggregates skate and hake complexes using survey data
  5. adjusts value of species for inflation

output

#comland <- readRDS(here::here("output","comland_meatwt_deflated_EPU.Rds"))
load(here::here("output","comland_meatwt_deflated_EPU.RData"))
head(comland)

Column Headings:

  • QY - Quarter year (1,2,3,4)
  • GEAR - aggreated gear type comprised of NEGEAR codes (See below)
